      <!-- Who Should Consider -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who Should Consider an Adjustment Loan?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          An Adjustment Loan may be suitable if you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          <li><strong>Desire Short-Term Rate Security:</strong> Prefer fixed payments for shorter periods but are comfortable with periodic adjustments.</li>
          <li><strong>Seek Flexibility:</strong> Want the ability to adjust your loan terms or switch between interest-only and amortizing payments.</li>
          <li><strong>Are Open to Variable Rates:</strong> Prepared for potential increases or decreases in payments due to interest rate changes.</li>
          <li><strong>Plan for Financial Changes:</strong> Anticipate changes in income or expenses and want a loan that can adapt accordingly.</li>
        </ul>
